title: Danil Massurenko
text:
Danil Yuryevich Massurenko (; born 22 May 1999) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Khimki-M">FC Khimki-M</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Khimki">FC Khimki</a> on 10 March 2018 in a game against <a href="FC%20Shinnik%20Yaroslavl">FC Shinnik Yaroslavl</a>.
